WEBVTT

00:02:57.849 --> 00:03:00.320
So he didn't tell them about the circus,

00:03:00.344 --> 00:03:05.661
or about how he wrestled professionally
on evenings and weekends.

00:03:06.353 --> 00:03:08.973
He used a pseudonym like Bull Walker,

00:03:08.997 --> 00:03:10.926
or later, the Masked Marvel.

00:03:11.627 --> 00:03:15.135
He even kept it a secret that same year,

00:03:15.159 --> 00:03:18.518
when he was crowned
the Light Heavyweight Champion

00:03:18.542 --> 00:03:19.771
of the world.

00:03:21.313 --> 00:03:25.919
Over the years, John J. Bonica
lived these parallel lives.

00:03:26.515 --> 00:03:28.209
He was a wrestler;

00:03:28.233 --> 00:03:29.390
he was a doctor.

00:03:29.788 --> 00:03:31.310
He was a heel;